name: Vefilla Warung Pizza
address: F6JH+PM6, Jl. Raya Pengembungan, Bongkasa, Kec. Abiansemal, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80352, Indonesia
review 1: Vefilla Warung Pizza is the perfect place to stop by and get a quick bite to eat!! The menu offers some great classic choices with awesome food and refreshing drinks!!! My husband and I stopped by after going to the bali swings. The owner was so delightful! We ordered the Margherita and the chicken sausage pizza!!! Both were delicious!!! I highly recommend the ice lemon tea !!! Thanks again :)
review 2: What a lovely small warung. The manager is super friendly, menu is very simple as expected from a tiny place. Definitely worth coming and have a little something!
review 3: Bought couple of pizzas a week ago, affordable prices and tasty. recommended for sure.
